ward_active_status,16,V4000d03d0,93000d045f,;"Seu passe de recompensa de 5 dias está ativo. O coaching com IA já está disponível.";future_self_ai_reward_active_status,17,V4000d02fa,5c000d0352,;"你的 5 天奖励通行证已激活，现在可以使用 AI 辅导。";future_self_ai_prompt_2,9,V40018086b,62001808c9,;"What feels different in your body on that day?";future_self_ai_prompt_2,10,V4001808e8,6c00180950,;"Was fühlt sich an diesem Tag in deinem Körper anders an?";future_self_ai_prompt_2,11,V40018086b,62001808c9,;"What feels different in your body on that day?";future_self_ai_prompt_2,12,V4001808f3,6200180951,;"¿Qué se siente diferente en tu cuerpo ese día?";future_self_ai_prompt_2,13,V4001808f5,6e0018095f,;"Qu’est-ce qui semble différent dans ton corps ce jour-là ?";future_self_ai_prompt_2,14,V4001806ba,47001806fd,;"その日の身体感覚は今と何が違いますか？";future_self_ai_prompt_2,15,V4001806f8,4b0018073f,;"그날의 몸 상태는 지금과 무엇이 다른가요?";future_self_ai_prompt_2,16,V40018090b,6200180969,;"O que parece diferente no seu corpo nesse dia?";future_self_ai_prompt_2,17,V400180661,43001806a0,;"那一天你的身体感觉有什么不同？";future_self_ai_prompt_1,9,V4001707f0,7a00170866,;"When you open your eyes that morning\, what is the first thing you see?";future_self_ai_prompt_1,10,V40017086e,79001708e3,;"Wenn du an diesem Morgen die Augen öffnest\, was siehst du als Erstes?";future_self_ai_prompt_1,11,V4001707f0,7a00170866,;"When you open your eyes that morning\, what is the first thing you see?";future_self_ai_prompt_1,12,V400170881,71001708ee,;"Cuando abres los ojos esa mañana\, ¿qué es lo primero que ves?";future_self_ai_prompt_1,13,V400170870,84001708f0,;"Quand tu ouvres les yeux ce matin-là\, quelle est la première chose que tu vois ?";future_self_ai_prompt_1,14,V40017066f,4a001706b5,;"その朝、目を開けたとき最初に何が見えますか？";future_self_ai_prompt_1,15,V4001706a7,50001706f3,;"그날 아침 눈을 떴을 때 가장 먼저 뭐가 보이나요?";future_self_ai_prompt_1,16,V40017088e,7c00170906,;"Quando você abre os olhos naquela manhã\, qual é a primeira coisa que vê?";future_self_ai_prompt_1,17,V400170618,480017065c,;"那天早晨你睁开眼时，第一眼看到的是什么？";future_self_settings_data_title,9,V4005e2346,4d005e238f,;"Delete local data";future_self_settings_data_title,10,V4005e25f5,50005e2641,;"Lokale Daten löschen";future_self_settings_data_title,11,V4005e2346,4d005e238f,;"Delete local data";future_self_settings_data_title,12,V4005e2504,52005e2552,;"Eliminar datos locales";future_self_settings_data_title,13,V4005e25bf,59005e2614,;"Supprimer les données locales";future_self_settings_data_title,14,V4005e1be9,46005e1c2b,;"ローカルデータを削除";future_self_settings_data_title,15,V4005e1cd3,45005e1d14,;"로컬 데이터 삭제";future_self_settings_data_title,16,V4005e253a,50005e2586,;"Excluir dados locais";future_self_settings_data_title,17,V4005e1a79,42005e1ab7,;"删除本地数据";future_self_domain_health,9,V40041175c,3c00411794,;"Health";future_self_domain_health,10,V4004118ff,400041193b,;"Gesundheit";future_self_domain_health,11,V40041175c,3c00411794,;"Health";future_self_domain_health,12,V4004118a4,3b004118db,;"Salud";future_self_domain_health,13,V4004118e9,3b00411920,;"Santé";future_self_domain_health,14,V4004112b7,38004112eb,;"健康";future_self_domain_health,15,V400411350,3800411384,;"건강";future_self_domain_health,16,V4004118d1,3b00411908,;"Saúde";future_self_domain_health,17,V4004111d0,3800411204,;"健康";future_self_domain_self,9,V400441815,3800441849,;"Self";future_self_domain_self,10,V4004419be,3a004419f4,;"Selbst";future_self_domain_self,11,V400441815,3800441849,;"Self";future_self_domain_self,12,V40044195e,3600441990,;"Yo";future_self_domain_self,13,V4004419a3,37004419d6,;"Soi";future_self_domain_self,14,V400441363,3600441395,;"自分";future_self_domain_self,15,V4004413fc,360044142e,;"자아";future_self_domain_self,16,V40044198b,36004419bd,;"Eu";future_self_domain_self,17,V40044127c,36004412ae,;"自我";future_self_quick_win_dialog_body,9,V400260d1e,9c00260db6,;"It does not need to be dramatic. Leave one action that moved you a little closer to the dream.";future_self_quick_win_dialog_body,10,V400260e08,a400260ea8,;"Er muss nicht groß sein. Halte eine Handlung fest\, die dich deinem Traum ein Stück näher gebracht hat.";future_self_quick_win_dialog_body,11,V400260d1e,9c00260db6,;"It does not need to be dramatic. Leave one action that moved you a little closer to the dream.";future_self_quick_win_dialog_body,12,V400260de0,9100260e6d,;"No tiene que ser algo grande. Deja una acción que te acercó un poco más a tu sueño.";future_self_quick_win_dialog_body,13,V400260e19,a000260eb5,;"Pas besoin que ce soit spectaculaire. Laisse une action qui t’a rapproché un peu plus de ton rêve.";future_self_quick_win_dialog_body,14,V400260a8c,6300260aeb,;"大きなことでなくて大丈夫です。夢に少し近づけた行動を一つ残してみましょう。";future_self_quick_win_dialog_body,15,V400260aee,6e00260b58,;"거창하지 않아도 괜찮아요. 오늘 꿈에 조금 더 가까워지게 만든 행동 하나를 남겨보세요.";future_self_quick_win_dialog_body,16,V400260e05,9d00260e9e,;"Não precisa ser algo grande. Registre uma ação que levou você um pouco mais perto do seu sonho.";future_self_quick_win_dialog_body,17,V4002609fd,5700260a50,;"不需要很宏大。留下一个让你离梦想更近一点的小行动。";future_self_progress_msg_starting,9,V4004d1b65,94004d1bf5,;"It is okay to still be warming up. One small action today is enough to start a rhythm.";future_self_progress_msg_starting,10,V4004d1d40,ac004d1de8,;"Es ist okay\, wenn du noch am Anlaufen bist. Eine kleine Handlung heute reicht aus\, um den Rhythmus zu starten.";future_self_progress_msg_starting,11,V4004d1b65,94004d1bf5,;"It is okay to still be warming up. One small action today is enough to start a rhythm.";future_self_progress_msg_starting,12,V4004d1cd2,9c004d1d6a,;"No pasa nada si aún estás calentando motores. Una sola acción hoy basta para empezar el ritmo.";future_self_progress_msg_starting,13,V4004d1d1f,b8004d1dd3,;"Ce n’est pas grave si tu es encore en train de démarrer. Une seule petite action aujourd’hui suffit pour lancer le rythme.";future_self_progress_msg_starting,14,V4004d15fe,62004d165c,;"まだ助走の段階でも大丈夫です。今日の小さな行動ひとつで流れは始まります。";future_self_progress_msg_starting,15,V4004d16b3,68004d1717,;"아직 준비 단계여도 괜찮아요. 오늘 한 번 움직이면 흐름이 생기기 시작해요.";future_self_progress_msg_starting,16,V4004d1d06,9c004d1d9e,;"Tudo bem se você ainda estiver começando. Uma pequena ação hoje já basta para iniciar o ritmo.";future_self_progress_msg_starting,17,V4004d150a,5e004d1564,;"即使你还在起步阶段也没关系。今天一个小行动，就足够开始形成节奏。";future_self_settings_privacy_policy_action,9,V4005b224e,5a005b22a4,;"View privacy policy";future_self_settings_privacy_policy_action,10,V4005b24eb,64005b254b,;"Datenschutzrichtlinie ansehen";future_self_settings_privacy_policy_action,11,V4005b224e,5a005b22a4,;"View privacy policy";future_self_settings_privacy_policy_action,12,V4005b23fe,61005b245b,;"Ver política de privacidad";future_self_settings_privacy_policy_action,13,V4005b24a5,6b005b250c,;"Voir la politique de confidentialité";future_self_settings_privacy_policy_action,14,V4005b1b08,54005b1b58,;"プライバシーポリシーを見る";future_self_settings_privacy_policy_action,15,V4005b1bf5,52005b1c43,;"개인정보처리방침 보기";future_self_settings_privacy_policy_action,16,V4005b243c,62005b249a,;"Ver política de privacidade";future_self_settings_privacy_policy_action,17,V4005b19a3,4d005b19ec,;"查看隐私政策";+style:Theme.Already,28,V40001003f,c000601e0,;DTheme.Material3.DayNight.NoActionBar,android\:statusBarColor:@android\:color/transparent,android\:navigationBarColor:@android\:color/transparent,android\:windowLightStatusBar:true,android\:windowLightNavigationBar:true,;+xml:locales_config,29,F;network_security_config,30,F;data_extraction_rules,31,F;backup_rules,32,F;